{"type": "article", "id": 6754, "title": "Collar 吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-25T07:18:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234234wixgu8oZhdNyQzBb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自丹麦哥本哈根的设计品牌 GUBI 日前联手德国年轻设计师 Sebastian Herkner 推出了一款名为「Collar Lamp」的吊灯，亮相于今年的科隆国际家具展。Sebastian Herkner 以衣领为设计灵感，采用手工吹制的玻璃与铝材制作灯罩，使得整个灯罩凸显出多面体的立体美感，细节上也尽显新技术与传统手艺的融合。Collar Lamp 提供两种尺寸，黑、灰、古铜、沙滩以及鸽子等 5 种配色，既可以单独使用，也可以配套设计出不同的趣味空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234231qCRz1dxZkr0ABoEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523423221V0wjWXsNxgy6zi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234232zwSo1rG5JOP9QNKB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76894866\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342334A7dWpoLhVB1gKck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052342335lEy3OwBJoVWsKkg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75052632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}